description: When cubed gives number composed just of the digits 1, 2, 3, 4, 5.

mathematica: Do[ If[ Union[ Join[ {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}, IntegerDigits[n^3] ] ] == {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}, Print[n] ], {n, 0, 10^7} ]
